==Demographics==
In 2010, Waterflow reported a total population of 1,670 people.  823 were male, and 807 were female.  809 identified themselves as White, 12 identified themselves as Black, 3 identified themselves as Asian, 171 were Hispanic, and 743 were Navajo.  620 speak a language other than English at home.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/SAFFFacts?_event=Search&geo_id=04000US35&_geoContext=01000US%7C04000US35&_street=&_county=&_cityTown=&_state=&_zip=87421&_lang=en&_sse=on&ActiveGeoDiv=geoSelect&_useEV=&pctxt=fph&pgsl=040&_submenuId=factsheet_1&ds_name=ACS_2008_3YR_SAFF&_ci_nbr=null&qr_name=null&reg=null%3Anull&_keyword=&_industry=&show_2003_tab=&redirect=Y |title=87421 - Fact Sheet - American FactFinder |publisher=Factfinder.census.gov |date= |accessdate=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200210215324/http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/SAFFFacts?_event=Search&geo_id=04000US35&_geoContext=01000US%7C04000US35&_street=&_county=&_cityTown=&_state=&_zip=87421&_lang=en&_sse=on&ActiveGeoDiv=geoSelect&_useEV=&pctxt=fph&pgsl=040&_submenuId=factsheet_1&ds_name=ACS_2008_3YR_SAFF&_ci_nbr=null&qr_name=null&reg=null:null&_keyword=&_industry=&show_2003_tab=&redirect=Y |archive-date=2020-02-10 |url-status=dead }}</ref>  With 551 housing units and a land area of 8.323 sq. miles, there are approximately 190 people per sq. mile in Waterflow.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://newmexico.hometownlocator.com/zip-codes/data,zipcode,87421.cfm |title=87421 (Waterflow, NM 87421) Profile: Maps, Real Estate, Jobs, Schools |publisher=Newmexico.hometownlocator.com |date= |accessdate=2011-08-17}}</ref>

